title: Neon Illusion of Authority
description: Create a detailed image inspired by an otherworldly scene featuring an alien riot police robot. The robot stands tall and imposing in a futuristic landscape. It should be embellished with vibrant neon colours and intricate designs that convey an illusion of authority and power. The overall visual style should reflect the whimsical, surreal, and metaphorically dense characteristics typical of late 19th century Symbolism art using oil on canvas, bearing in mind that this combination results in a captivating and visually striking composition.
